 need keep accesspc loaded all time cutting back your
 extension habit can really help avoid crashes 


 rebuild desktop 

 desktop filedatabase holds all information necessary
 associate each file application created 
 lets system know what application should launched when you
 open given file what icons should display where 
 depending its size each application has one more
 representatives desktop file applications files
 move off your hard disk desktop file can become
 bloated corrupt think congress your mac 
 every so often its necessary throw bums out start 
 clean slate fortunately its easier rebuild desktop than
 defeat incumbent 
 
 one warning rebuilding desktop erase all comments
 youve stored get info boxes under system maurice
 volaskis freeware init commentkeeper retain those comments
 across rebuild commentkeeper also works system only 
 apples desktop manager extension also installed 
 
 rebuild desktop restart your mac your
 extensions finish loading depress command option keys 
 youll presented dialog box asking you want rebuild
 desktop warning you could take few minutes 
 click ok take more than few minutes more files you
 have longer take youre running system you may
 want turn off multifinder before trying rebuild desktop
 
 youre experiencing definite problems just doing
 preventive maintenance you may want use fifth generations
 freeware init desktop reset desktop reset completely deletes 
 desktop file before rebuilding thus eliminating possibly
 corrupt data structures 


 zap pram reset clock 

 all macs from original k thin mac quadra 
 contain small amount battery powered ram hold certain
 settings properly move cpu rather than disk
 which disk boot from unfortunately parameter
 ram can become corrupted cause unexplained crashes reset
 under system hold down command option p r keys
 while restarting your mac under system hold down command
 option shift keys while selecting control panel from 
 apple menu click yes when asked you want zap parameter
 ram since youve erased almost all settings general
 control panel you should now reset them whatever you want
 
 one setting zapping pram does erase 
 date time since internal clock macintosh 
 notoriously inaccurate youll probably want take 
 opportunity reset anyway


 resize system heap 

 even after rethinking extensions per step two most
 people still have least half row icons march across 
 bottom screen every time restart all 
 extensions most applications too need space section 
 memory called system heap system heap isnt big enough
 comfortably accommodate all programs want piece 
 all start playing king mountain system heap
 knocking each other off get bigger pieces themselves 
 trying climb back after get knocked off all 
 fighting amongst programs severely degrades system performance
 almost inevitably crashes mac
 
 youre using system your macintosh automatically
 resize system heap necessary youre running system 
 its important set your system heap size large enough manage
 all your extensions applications default size set
 k way too small most macs any extensions all 
 system heap size stored normally noneditable boot
 blocks every system disk bill steinbergs freeware utility
 bootman only lets you resize your system heap even checks
 how much memory your heap already using so can tell how much
 needs allocated youre running system get bootman
 use amazed how infrequently your macintosh crashes


