 your system file temporary suitcase
 trash system file your hard disk also trash 
 finder multifinder da handler all other standard apple 
 extensions like control panel chooser all 
 replaced new installation youre running 
 installing system move everything extensions 
 control panels preferences folders top level 
 system folder
 rename system folder any name other than system folder 
 fine
 doubleclick installer script your system disk 
 choose customize select appropriate software your 
 model mac printer you could do easy install instead 
 only add lot extensions code you dont 
 need waste your memory disk space
 once installation finished move everything from 
 temporary folder you created step new system 
 folder youre asked you want replace anything you 
 forgot take something out step youll need replace 
 things individually until you find duplicate piece 
 reinstall any fonts das you removed step 
 reboot you should now have clean defragmented system file 
 takes up less memory disk space much more stable 
 system overall


 disk utilities 

 much like system files hard disks have data structures 
 occasionally become corrupted affecting performance even
 causing data loss apple includes disk first aid simple utility
 detecting repairing hard disk problems its system
 disks its also available anonymous ftp from ftpapplecom 
 directory dtsmacsyssofthdsc even you have earlier 
 version you should get latest version from ftpapplecom
 run all your hard disks
 
 several companies have released payware disk utilities 
 detect repair considerably more problems than disk first aid
 though interestingly none them detect repair everything
 disk first aid does three most effective general
 work central points mactools deluxe fifth generations
 public utilites symantecs norton utilities macintosh
 department work group should have all well
 disk first aid since none them fix everything others do 
 individuals mactools street about half price 
 norton street public utilities street so features
 ease use being roughly equal i recommend mactools
 
 all products occasionally encounter problems 
 cant fix when happens its time backup 
 reformat 


 backing up 

 one part preventative maintenance should 
 done lot more often than every three months simplest back
 up merely copy all files your hard disk onto floppies
 other removable media you keep your data files separate
 from your application support files its easy only back
 up those folders which change frequently nonetheless every three
 months you should do complete backup your hard disk 
 
 number programs available make backing up
 easier apple included very basic full backup application 
 system performas apple ships new apple backup
 utility can backup entire disk just system folder
 onto floppies previously mentioned norton utilities 
 mac mactools deluxe include more powerful floppy backup
 utilities incorporate compression incremental backups
 
 finally youre lucky enough have tape drive network
 server removable media device use backups you should
 check out more powerful payware utilities redux street
 doesnt support tape drives diskfit pro street 
 freely available backup utilities other than old hd
 backup from system 


 disk defragmentation 

 disks fill up gets harder harder find enough free
 space same place write large files therefore 
 operating system often split larger files pieces 
 stored different places your hard disk files become more
 more fragmented performance can degrade several
 ways defragment hard disk
 
 most tedious cheapest method backup all your
 files erase hard disk you might well reformat while
 youre see question restore all files
 
 number payware utilities including norton utilities 
 mac mac tools deluxe can defragment disk place ie
 without erasing although ads all products brag
 about safety once youve bought software opened 
 shrinkwrap all warn you back up your disk before
 defragmenting case something does go wrong 
 freeware shareware disk defragmenters so please dont annoy 
 net asking one 


 reformat your hard disk 

 just floppy disk needs initialized before use so 
 hard disk must formatted before can hold data you dont
 need reformat every three months when your system 
 crashing matter what you try reformatting ultimate means
 wiping slate clean reformatting your hard disk may even
